{"tid":1252878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際特赦組織+陳方安生+醫護法律界，夠料出份清算聲明喇掛？","createTime":"2019-06-23T09:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T13:34:58.000Z","uid":267881,"like":128,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"47b6ce03c75704de60087ca83ccc69547100d60e","tid":1252878,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:11:03.000Z","msg":"國際特赦組織確認香港警察違反人權法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1247785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1247785</a><br />\n<br />\n前政務司司長陳方安生致林鄭月娥公開信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1250929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1250929</a><br />\n<br />\n【監警10年】淪無牙老虎 監警會質詢警權 警方接受率0%<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1240187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1240187</a><br />\n<br />\n近日，從本港醫護界、法律界、新聞界、政界、國際特赦組織、破紀錄二百萬人遊行、無數被欺壓的香港市民的論述，已有大量證據顯示警隊濫權濫捕、制度腐敗、投訴機制失效，淪為極權政府打壓反對聲音的維穩工具，市民對此表示極度不滿和憂慮，有見及此，本人建議出一份聲明，提倡：<br />\n<br />\n1 向全世界媒體詳述香港警方犯罪情況<br />\n2 向外國提供個人資料阻礙其申請國籍和入境<br />\n3 獨立調查委員會追究612涉事警員法律責任<br />\n4 辭退所有縱容犯罪的警隊領導層<br />\n5 改善警校課程和設立警員再培訓班<br />\n6 成立獨立監管局跟進違規個案，警方須配合<br />\n7 賦與獨立監管局權力審查警員是否政治中立<br />\n8 完全捨棄舊有的投訴機制<br />\n9 所有當值警員(臥底除外)必須配戴委任證<br />\n10 警員編號字體增大一倍，展視在胸前和背部<br />\n11 優先晉升盡忠職守，沒違紀行為的警員<br />\n<br />\n本人建議盡快草擬聲明內容並請求各界聯署，志在清除瘀血，還警隊清白者清白，重建警隊國際形象，重拾市民對警隊信心，讓社會回歸正道，停止撕裂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關行動：<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織發起全球聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1250392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1250392</a><br />\n[一齊send] 推黑警上聯合國人權理事會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251321</a><br />\n[法律撚] 追究起底人士 = 只係兇鳩你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1252488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1252488</a><br />\n<br />\n表揚清白、英勇警察：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212345</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1214460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1214460</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219611</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223139</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1237056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1237056</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1236122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1236122</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1237395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1237395</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241106</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1249050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1249050</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1252832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1252832</a>"},{"pid":"dae6d7f3743307ef09b8605ffda7375050f68717","tid":1252878,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98741ddec977cb2c2e034760d03bf92f5f8053c7","tid":1252878,"uid":18959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"仲有多個前官員"},{"pid":"4d235cea98be43cc9161e67c30cc498d4a91c544","tid":1252878,"uid":138051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:19:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0372e13056d44e1b5b876dfe9a0a724377d1150d","tid":1252878,"uid":6980,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n重點放喺幫警隊重振聲威 清除瘀血<br />\n件事個feel冇咁對立<br />\n大眾接受程度應該會高啲<br />\n要搶先班狗企喺道德高地先<br />\n咁長期抗爭打輿論戰先有得贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e514cb2cf3ffae1f5ddd139ab04968bd086aa3b","tid":1252878,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98741ddec977cb2c2e034760d03bf92f5f8053c7","tid":1252878,"uid":18959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"仲有多個前官員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:22:39.000Z",